《'''遥不可及'''》（{{lang-en|''So Far Away''}}）是由荷兰[[音乐制作人|音乐制作人]][[马丁·盖瑞斯|马丁·盖瑞斯]]和法国音乐制作人[[大衛·庫塔_(DJ)|大卫·库塔]]主唱，英国歌手{{tsl|en|Jamie Scott|杰米·斯科特|杰米·斯科特}}和荷兰歌手罗米·迪亚伴唱的歌曲。2017年12月1日，歌曲通过[[戳印唱片|戳印唱片]]正式发行，由斯科特、{{le|Poo Bear}}、盖瑞斯、库塔和{{tsl|en|Giorgio Tuinfort|乔治·图伊福特|乔治·图伊福特}}作词作曲，后三人负责制作。《遥不可及》是库塔第七张录音室专辑《{{tsl|en|7 (David Guetta album)|7 (大卫·库塔专辑)|7}}》中的附赠曲目，并在2017年[[明日世界电子音乐节|明日世界电子音乐节]]中由盖瑞斯首次演唱。

==背景==
2017年7月30日，在明日世界电子音乐节的主舞台上，盖瑞斯邀请库塔首次演唱了《遥不可及》。歌曲的最初版本由英国歌手[[艾丽·高登|艾丽·高登]]担任女声伴唱<ref>{{cite news|last=Bein|first=Kat|title=David Guetta Joined Martin Garrix at Tomorrowland 2017, Debuted Collab With Ellie Goulding: Watch|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/7882147/david-guetta-martin-garrix-tomorrowland-2017-ellie-goulding|work=Billboard|date=2017-07-31|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2019-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190417120434/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/7882147/david-guetta-martin-garrix-tomorrowland-2017-ellie-goulding|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Powell|first=Karlie|title=Watch Martin Garrix Close Out Tomorrowland 2017's Main Stage|url=http://www.youredm.com/2017/07/31/watch-martin-garrix-close-tomorrowland-2017s-main-stage/|work=Your EDM|date=2017-07-31|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2019-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190408184106/https://www.youredm.com/2017/07/31/watch-martin-garrix-close-tomorrowland-2017s-main-stage/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。8月21日，在[[伊维萨岛|伊维萨岛]]的一次表演中，盖瑞斯和库塔又一次演唱了该歌曲<ref>{{cite news|last=Erik|title=Martin Garrix Brought Out David Guetta In Ibiza Last Night To Play Upcoming Collaboration|url=https://www.edmsauce.com/2017/08/22/martin-garrix-brought-david-guetta-ibiza-last-night-play-upcoming-collaboration/|work=EDM Sauce|date=2017-08-22|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2019-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190408184057/https://www.edmsauce.com/2017/08/22/martin-garrix-brought-david-guetta-ibiza-last-night-play-upcoming-collaboration/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[Instagram|Instagram]]上，有人上传了一段由展台内人员拍摄的短片<ref>{{cite news|last=Rafter|first=Andrew|title=Martin Garrix teases David Guetta collaboration during Ibiza show|url=https://djmag.com/news/martin-garrix-teases-david-guetta-collaboration-during-ibiza-show|work=[[DJ雜誌|DJ Mag]]|date=2017-08-24|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2019-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190411092607/https://djmag.com/news/martin-garrix-teases-david-guetta-collaboration-during-ibiza-show|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Meadow|first=Matthew|title=Martin Garrix Continues To Hype New Collab With David Guetta, Brings Him Out In Ibiza|url=http://www.youredm.com/2017/08/23/martin-garrix-continues-hype-new-collab-david-guetta-brings-ibiza/|work=Your EDM|date=2017-08-23|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2019-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190408184104/https://www.youredm.com/2017/08/23/martin-garrix-continues-hype-new-collab-david-guetta-brings-ibiza/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在演出前，盖瑞斯向{{le|Capital FM|Capital (radio network)}}介绍了这首歌，认为其“非常适合电台”并将很快发行<ref>{{cite news|title=Martin Garrix Teased A New Collab With David Guetta & A Mystery Vocalist And We NEED To Know Who It Is|url=http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/martin-garrix/news/new-song-david-guetta/|work=Capital|date=2017-08-25|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2017-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206215857/http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/martin-garrix/news/new-song-david-guetta/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月19日，盖瑞斯通过Instagram Stories发布了一个简短的《遥不可及》录音室预告片，并暗示将在不久发行<ref>{{cite news|last=DJ Mag Staff|title=Martin Garrix teases David Guetta collab ahead of official release|url=https://djmag.com/news/martin-garrix-teases-david-guetta-collab-ahead-official-release|work=DJ Mag|date=2017-11-21|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2017-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206210451/https://djmag.com/news/martin-garrix-teases-david-guetta-collab-ahead-official-release|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Powell|first=Karlie|title=Martin Garrix Teases David Guetta Collab Ahead Of Its Release [Listen]|url=http://www.youredm.com/2017/11/19/martin-garrix-teases-david-guetta-collab-ahead-release-listen/|work=Your EDM|date=2017-11-19|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2017-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206215806/http://www.youredm.com/2017/11/19/martin-garrix-teases-david-guetta-collab-ahead-release-listen/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

11月22日，盖瑞斯在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上回复艾丽·高登粉丝时透露，高登将不再为《遥不可及》献唱，艾丽·高登在Twitter上对盖瑞斯的预告片进行了评论<ref>{{cite news|last=Rodriguez|first=Christopher|title=Martin Garrix And David Guetta Collaboration No Longer Includes Ellie Goulding|url=http://www.edmtunes.com/2017/11/ellie-goulding-martin-garrix-david-guetta/|work=EDM Sauce|date=2017-11-22|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2017-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206205120/http://www.edmtunes.com/2017/11/ellie-goulding-martin-garrix-david-guetta/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。高登在一系列推文中承认，她的管理层和唱片公司都很不满，因为盖瑞斯在明日世界电子音乐节演唱了这首歌，而她甚至还没听过最终版本，这导致了她的人声从曲目上被删去，但她强调她不是幕后推手<ref>{{cite news|last=Rafter|first=Andrew|title=Ellie Goulding won't be appearing on Martin Garrix & David Guetta's new collaboration, 'So Far Away'|url=https://djmag.com/news/ellie-goulding-wont-be-appearing-martin-garrix-david-guettas-new-collaboration-so-far-away|work=DJ Mag|date=2017-11-30|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2017-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171204032856/https://djmag.com/news/ellie-goulding-wont-be-appearing-martin-garrix-david-guettas-new-collaboration-so-far-away|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Meadow|first=Matthew|title=Martin Garrix Confirms "So Far Away" Is No Longer With Ellie Goulding|url=http://www.youredm.com/2017/11/27/martin-garrix-confirms-far-away-no-longer-ellie-goulding/|work=Your EDM|date=2017-11-27|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2017-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206210508/http://www.youredm.com/2017/11/27/martin-garrix-confirms-far-away-no-longer-ellie-goulding/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她在Twitter上写道，盖瑞斯“她不想发行歌曲”的声明是“完全虚假和不公平的”<ref>{{cite news|last=Bein|first=Kat|title=Ellie Goulding Won't Appear On Martin Garrix & David Guetta Collab 'So Far Away'|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8053976/ellie-goulding-dropped-martin-garrix-david-guetta-collab|work=Billboard|date=2017-11-29|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2017-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171207083130/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8053976/ellie-goulding-dropped-martin-garrix-david-guetta-collab|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Stevo|title=Martin Garrix Confirms "So Far Away" With Ellie Goulding Is No Longer Being Released|url=https://www.edmsauce.com/2017/11/27/martin-garrix-confirms-far-away-ellie-goulding-no-longer-released/|work=EDM Sauce|date=2017-11-27|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2017-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206205229/https://www.edmsauce.com/2017/11/27/martin-garrix-confirms-far-away-ellie-goulding-no-longer-released/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

11月26日，盖瑞斯在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上回复粉丝关于哪首歌曲首先发行的问题时，证实了《遥不可及》将和{{le|AREA21}}歌曲《Glad You Came》于同一天发行<ref>{{cite news|last=Bein|first=Kat|title=Martin Garrix Promises Long-Teased Tracks Coming Soon|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8046997/martin-garrix-new-songs-david-guetta-ellie-goulding-conor-maynard|work=Billboard|date=2017-11-27|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2017-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171130061905/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8046997/martin-garrix-new-songs-david-guetta-ellie-goulding-conor-maynard|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=DJ Mag Staff|title=Martin Garrix to release two new songs on the same day very soon|url=https://djmag.com/news/martin-garrix-release-two-new-songs-same-day-very-soon|work=DJ Mag|date=2017-11-27|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2017-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206210153/https://djmag.com/news/martin-garrix-release-two-new-songs-same-day-very-soon|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1月29日，盖瑞斯在社交媒体上发布了官方预告片，透露了歌曲的发行日期及伴唱歌手：杰米·斯科特（Jamie Scott）和罗米·迪亚（Romy Dya），后者曾在《遥不可及》的演示版中献唱<ref>{{cite news|last=Meadow|first=Matthew|title=First Listen: Martin Garrix Shares HQ Teaser Of New Collab With David Guetta|url=http://www.youredm.com/2017/11/29/first-listen-martin-garrix-shares-hq-teaser-new-collab-david-guetta/|work=Your EDM|date=2017-11-29|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2017-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206220208/http://www.youredm.com/2017/11/29/first-listen-martin-garrix-shares-hq-teaser-new-collab-david-guetta/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==评论==
《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|公告牌]]》的凯特·贝因（Kat Bein）称《遥不可及》是“一首优美的未来流行歌曲”。他赞扬称Dya提供了一场“脆弱但强大”的表演<ref>{{cite news|last=Bein|first=Kat|title=Martin Garrix's David Guetta Collab 'So Far Away' Is a Beautiful Future-Pop Ballad: Watch|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8054864/martin-garrix-david-guetta-so-far-away-watch|work=Billboard|date=2017-12-01|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2018-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180202110244/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8054864/martin-garrix-david-guetta-so-far-away-watch|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《Your EDM》的马修·梅多（Matthew Meadow）也写道，Dya和斯科特做了一项“了不起的工作”，让听众们激情澎湃。他批评鼓点缺乏独创性，称之为《[[害怕寂寞|害怕寂寞]]2.0》<ref>{{cite news|last=Meadow|first=Matthew|title=Martin Garrix Finally Releases David Guetta Collaboration, "So Far Away"|url=http://www.youredm.com/2017/11/30/martin-garrix-finally-releases-david-guetta-collaboration-far-away/|work=Your EDM|date=2017-11-30|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2017-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206220007/http://www.youredm.com/2017/11/30/martin-garrix-finally-releases-david-guetta-collaboration-far-away/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《EDM Sauce》的埃里克也给出了类似的评论，他写道：“没有（艾丽·高登），这首歌很可能不会获得同程度的成功，因为没有什么绝对的独创性。”他还写道，这首歌“具有巨大的主流吸引力”，并且“正是美国广播观众目前所期待发行的”<ref>{{cite news|last=Erik|title=Martin Garrix and David Guetta Finally Release 'So Far Away'|url=https://www.edmsauce.com/2017/11/30/martin-garrix-david-guetta-finally-release-far-away/|work=EDM Sauce|date=2017-11-30|accessdate=2017-12-06|archive-date=2017-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206202332/https://www.edmsauce.com/2017/11/30/martin-garrix-david-guetta-finally-release-far-away/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

